QuestData.Title: Hungry Mouths To Feed
QuestData.Description:
We don't have much in de way of supplies right now.
Mojambo and his gang will be back to finish us off, of dat I'm sure. But without food and supplies, dere will be none of us alive for dem to kill.
Our cook is looking for someone to help gather supplies so we can feed de camp.
Speak with him and see if you can find what he's looking for.
